headline: WOODWARD PARK PARTNERS ADVISES SALUS GROUP IN ITS SALE TO NFP, A WHOLLY OWNED SUBSIDIARY OF AON
summary: Woodward Park Partners is pleased to announce that its client, Benefits Partner, LLC dba Salus Group ("Salus Group"), has been acquired by NFP, a wholly owned subsidiary of Aon (NYSE: AON). Salus Group is a leading independent benefits consulting, brokerage and administration firm.
